---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Vie à l'école">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="relative h-64 md:h-80 overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
        <img
            src="/assets/images/Photo01.jpg"
            alt="Vie à l'école"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <h1
                class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight drop-shadow-md text-center px-4"
            >
                Vie à l'école
            </h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
            <!-- Section 1: Implication des Parents -->
            <div class="mb-20">
                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 flex items-center"
                    style="font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;"
                >
                    <span class="bg-amber-100 p-2 rounded-full mr-4 text-2xl"
                        >👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</span
                    >
                    L'Implication des Parents
                </h2>

                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center mb-8">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-2/2">
                        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
                            L’école compte sur la collaboration des parents qui
                            sont régulièrement invités à participer à la vie de
                            l’école. Cette implication prend notamment les
                            formes suivantes :
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                        <img
                            src="/assets/images/Photo10.jpg"
                            alt="Implication des parents"
                            class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-xl object-cover"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-6">
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 mt-1"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="ml-4 text-slate-600">
                            Participation à la présentation de la vertu du mois
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 mt-1"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="ml-4 text-slate-600">
                            Soirée spirituelle pour les parents
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 mt-1"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="ml-4 text-slate-600">
                            Conférences sur l’éducation
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 mt-1"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="ml-4 text-slate-600">Préceptorat</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 mt-1"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="ml-4 text-slate-600">
                            Organisation du marché de Noël (dernier samedi de
                            novembre)
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 mt-1"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="ml-4 text-slate-600">
                            Parent délégué (2 par classe)
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 mt-1"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="ml-4 text-slate-600">
                            Accompagnements (gymnase, sorties)
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 mt-1"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="ml-4 text-slate-600">
                            Entretien des locaux (samedi matin tous les 2 mois)
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <!-- Section 2: Rythme Scolaire -->
                <div
                    class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 h-full"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center"
                        style="font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;"
                    >
                        <span class="bg-blue-100 p-2 rounded-full mr-4 text-xl"
                            >⏰</span
                        >
                        Rythme Scolaire
                    </h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800">
                                Horaires de semaine
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-600">
                                Lundi, mardi, jeudi, vendredi : <br /><span
                                    class="font-medium"
                                    >8h45-12h et 13h30-16h30</span
                                >
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800">
                                Samedis travaillés
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-600">
                                +12 samedis par an (CP au CM2) : <br /><span
                                    class="font-medium">9h-12h</span
                                >
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">
                                Le calendrier est donné en début d’année.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800">Vacances</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-600">
                                Calendrier de l’Education nationale, zone C.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Section 3: Repas -->
                <div
                    class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 h-full"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center"
                        style="font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;"
                    >
                        <span class="bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-full mr-4 text-xl"
                            >🍽️</span
                        >
                        Paniers Repas
                    </h2>
                    <div class="prose prose-slate text-slate-600">
                        <p>
                            Il n’y a pas de cantine, toutefois il est possible
                            d’apporter son <strong>« panier-repas »</strong> pour
                            déjeuner sur place.
                        </p>
                        <div
                            class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 my-4"
                        >
                            <p class="text-sm">
                                ⚠️ <span class="font-bold">Important :</span> Il faut
                                en faire la demande et s'être inscrit car la capacité
                                d'accueil est limitée.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <p>
                            L’organisation pratique des paniers-repas fait
                            l’objet d’une circulaire distribuée en juin.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
